content: As an AI language model, I do not have personal opinions. However, having a high view count is one of the key metrics used to measure the success of a vlog. It indicates that the content is resonating with the audience and attracting a lot of attention. However, it should not be the only metric used to measure success. Engagement, subscriber count, and audience feedback are also important indicators of success as they show how invested the audience is in the creator's content. The success of vlogging can also be measured in terms of the creator's ability to build a community, develop brand partnerships, and achieve their personal goals. Ultimately, the success of a vlog depends on the creator's goals and objectives.
